data.description: This exquisite 4-bedroom home, situated in a highly sought-after area, is the epitome of comfort and functionality, featuring shutters throughout the house for added charm and practicality.  The main floor features a thoughtfully designed layout, including a spacious living room, formal entertaining and a guest bedroom and bathroom. The well-equipped kitchen featuring modern appliances and a central island.  As you ascend the stairs, you'll be greeted by a spacious loft, which can serve as an additional living area, a home office, or a playroom, providing endless possibilities.The master bedroom offers ample space, a walk-in closet, and a private en-suite bathroom for ultimate comfort.Two additional bedrooms on this level are perfect for guests, complete with a shared full bathroom to cater to their needs.The home boasts excellent curb appeal with well-maintained landscaping, a gazebo in the backyard offers a delightful retreat for cooling off during the summer and a 8x10 shed.
